---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About Us — Jakob Simon Zürich">
  <section class="relative h-[55vh] min-h-[420px]">
    <img src="/js-assets/JakobSimon0394.webp" alt="" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40"></div>
    <div class="relative h-full flex items-center justify-center">
      <h1 class="heading-display text-white">About Us</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="container-js max-w-3xl">
      <blockquote class="font-serif text-2xl md:text-3xl leading-snug italic text-center mb-5 fade-up">
        "For beautiful eyes, look for the good in others; for beautiful lips, speak only words of kindness; and for poise, walk with the knowledge that you are never alone."
      </blockquote>
      <p class="text-center eyebrow text-navy fade-up">— Audrey Hepburn</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pb-24">
    <div class="container-js grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <img src="/js-assets/IMG_2737_3.jpg" alt="" class="w-full fade-up" />
      <div class="fade-up space-y-5 text-[15px] leading-[1.85] font-light text-black/80">
        <p>Black-and-white films, Frank Sinatra, an attentive door held open.</p>
        <p>We love the elegance of the 60s. At Jakob Simon, the classic image of lady and gentleman is by no means outdated — it reflects values and behaviour that transcend any trend.</p>
        <p>Respectful manners, appreciation of others, hospitality, and respect for personality are some of the values we represent as a brand and toward our customers.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24 bg-[#f8f8f4]">
    <div class="container-js max-w-3xl text-center">
      <p class="eyebrow text-navy mb-4 fade-up">Our Vision</p>
      <h2 class="heading-section mb-8 fade-up">Leading the upper premium segment.</h2>
      <div class="space-y-5 text-[15px] leading-[1.85] font-light text-black/80 fade-up">
        <p>Our vision at Jakob Simon is to make the Zurich luxury label a leading brand in the upper premium segment, in the elegant style of "old money".</p>
        <p>Stylistic features as well as values and brand personality are reflected at every customer touchpoint.</p>
        <p>We offer a first-class shopping experience and a high level of customer satisfaction. Our products are manufactured with great care in renowned ateliers in Italy.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="container-js max-w-3xl text-center">
      <p class="eyebrow text-navy mb-4 fade-up">Our Mission</p>
      <h2 class="heading-section mb-8 fade-up">Styling excellence.</h2>
      <p class="text-[15px] leading-[1.85] font-light text-black/80 mb-9 fade-up">
        We create an environment of well-being. True to the motto "Excellently styled at any age and for any occasion", we take our customers on a journey of timeless elegance — flattering both the eye and the soul.
      </p>
      <a href="/collections/all" class="btn-outline fade-up">Discover the collection</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
